    Users.prototype.all = function(params, fn) {
      var cb, data;
      if (params == null) {
        params = {};
      }
      if (fn == null) {
        fn = null;
      }
      if ('function' === typeof params) {
        fn = params;
        params = {};
      }
      this.debug("Users::all()");
      if (params.page == null) {
        params.page = 1;
      }
      if (params.per_page == null) {
        params.per_page = 100;
      }
      data = [];
      cb = (function(_this) {
        return function(err, retData) {
          if (err) {
            if (fn) {
              return fn(retData || data);
            }

            if (fn) {

            }
          }
        };
      })(this);

    };
